casebody.data:
Hadassa HELINSKI, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Paul Brian HELINSKI, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2001 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 30, 2017 SALTER, EMAS and LOGUE, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of certiorari, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.

Upon consideration of petitioner's motion for appellate attorney's fees, it is ordered that said motion is hereby denied.

Petitioner's motion to expedite is hereby denied as moot.
